CLEANLOGS-UNIX#RMSTDLIST-UNIX
 SCRIPTNAME "$UNISON_DIR/bin/rmstdlist 10;rc=`ls -l $UNISON_DIR | grep -w methods | wc -l | tr -d \" \"`;if [ $rc -eq 0 ];then exit 0;fi;rc1=`ls -l $UNISON_DIR/methods | grep -w traces | wc -l | tr -d \" \"`;if [ $rc1 -eq 0 ];then exit 0;fi;rc2=`ls -l $UNISON_DIR/methods/traces | grep -w trace-r3batch.log | wc -l | tr -d \" \"`;if [ $rc2 -eq 0 ];then exit 0;fi;cp $UNISON_DIR/methods/traces/trace-r3batch.log $UNISON_DIR/methods/traces/bkp-trace-r3batch.`date +%Y%m%d`;echo >$UNISON_DIR/methods/traces/trace-r3batch.log;ls -l $UNISON_DIR/methods/traces/;find $UNISON_DIR/methods/traces/bkp-trace-r3batch* -ctime +1 -exec rm {} \;"
 STREAMLOGON maestro
 DESCRIPTION "Added by composer."
 TASKTYPE UNIX
 RECOVERY STOP

TESTUNIX#CHECKVERSION
 DOCOMMAND "echo \"TWS version:\"; cat /etc/TWS/TWSRegistry.dat|sort|uniq|grep maestro_DN_Package |cut -f2 -d \"=\"|cut -f2-4 -d \".\"; echo \"TWS fixpack:\"; cat /etc/TWS/TWSRegistry.dat|sort|uniq|grep maestro_DN_FixpackName|cut -f5 -d \".\"|tail -1; echo \"TWS type:\"; cat /etc/TWS/TWSRegistry.dat|sort|uniq|grep maestro_DN_Agent |cut -f2 -d \"=\"|cut -f2 -d \"=\""
 STREAMLOGON root
 TASKTYPE UNIX
 RECOVERY STOP


TESTUNIX#PINGMASTER
 DOCOMMAND "hostname;host ADCULNARTWSP1;exit 0"
 STREAMLOGON maestro
 DESCRIPTION "Added by composer."
 TASKTYPE UNIX
 RECOVERY STOP

 STREAMLOGON root
